{"tid":1459710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"到底大家搭鐵幾時識得跳？","createTime":"2019-08-12T19:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T20:36:28.000Z","uid":260806,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d5791af44b76f174ea44eb99c9fd774a35d46b83","tid":1459710,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqX3UVE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqX3UVE.png&h=8fa965ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我真係火滾<br />\n點解仲要畀錢搭閪鐵<br />\n其實唔係個個位都有人捉<br />\n其實未必需要喺閘度跳（真係好多位都得）<br />\n跳出比跳入風險低<br />\n跳入如果被捉就馬上掙脫搵位跳出<br />\n我就唔信個黃衫仔會衝出來追<br />\n有機會就跳啊各位<br />\n唔好再諗咁多<br />\n今時今日就算入閘後都會發生太古電梯追打事件<br />\n命都就來冇喇<br />\n仲理你係咪畀錢買飛？"},{"pid":"4771f5d262d0df6705f5bbfe01ca97c6baf25c23","tid":1459710,"uid":59016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7196663ad139e87e1dc33d519f865d30522a7e","tid":1459710,"uid":19445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:26:23.000Z","msg":"聽日搭鐵入機場既 唔撚好再益狗鐵 跳啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459574</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n竟然仲排隊買飛 留錢買水好過啦"},{"pid":"35364b8056cd4069a743c76df023c7674d7fcbf4","tid":1459710,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a096eaa331bbeab3d8a61fa2d15136f9897711","tid":1459710,"uid":34069,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:26:47.000Z","msg":"有大把cam 秋後算帳<br />\n除非好多人咁做 什至開埋門"},{"pid":"2fb4a821551bfa0f30d31fb53c900d802c9e5d67","tid":1459710,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:28:08.000Z","msg":"唔跳都用下長者八達通"},{"pid":"de8654cde791ee75b12187c0af494ef93e1ee202","tid":145971